h AuthMode=picod: verify public key injected\n  Line 305:   - Inject public key if AuthMode=picod\n  Line 329:   - Test AuthMode=picod with public key injection\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md:\n  Line 183:    - Empty `AuthMode`: Default to `\"picod\"`\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go:\n  Line 251: \t\t\t\t\tAuthMode:           AuthModePicoD,\n  Line 393: \tif AuthModePicoD != \"picod\" {\n  Line 394: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected AuthModePicoD to be 'picod', got '%s'\", AuthModePicoD)\n  Line 435: \t\t\t\t\tAuthMode:           AuthModePicoD,\n  Line 650: \tif DefaultAuthMode != AuthModePicoD {\n  Line 651: \t\tt.Errorf(\"DefaultAuthMode: expected %s, got %s\", AuthModePicoD, DefaultAuthMode)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go:\n  Line 21: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n  Line 25: \t// AuthModePicoD indicates pico authentication mode.\n  Line 26: \tAuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n  Line 169: \tDefaultAuthMode = AuthModePicoD\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md:\n  Line 24:   - Constants: `AuthModePicoD`, `AuthModeNone`\n  Line 25:   - Verify: `grep -q \"AuthModePicoD\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n  Line 127:   - Value: `AuthModePicoD`\n  Line 218: | T1.2 | `grep -q \"AuthModePicoD\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md:\n  Line 61: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n  Line 65:     // AuthModePicoD indicates pico authentication mode.\n  Line 66:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n  Line 223:     DefaultAuthMode = AuthModePicoD\n  Line 245: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode` | `picod` / `none` | Pod |\n  Line 268: | Invalid AuthModeType | Value not `picod`/`none` | API server rejects with 400 |\n  Line 316:         {\"PicoD\", AuthModePicoD, \"picod\"},\n  Line 390:     if DefaultAuthMode != AuthModePicoD {\n  Line 433:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n  Line 505:     DefaultAuthMode  = AuthModePicoD\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md:\n  Line 18: - `AuthModeType` µ×ÜõĖŠ’╝łpicod/none’╝ē\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md:\n  Line 29: - `AuthModeType`: Enum for picod/none\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md:\n  Line 30:   - `AuthMode AuthModeType` (default: picod, enum: picod|none)\n  Line 60:   - Constants: `AuthModePicoD = \"picod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`\n  Line 113:   - Verify `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n  Line 138:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` on AuthMode\n  Line 139:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` on AuthMode\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 79:   - `AuthMode AuthModeType` with JSON tag `authMode` (optional, default picod)\n  Line 100:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` marker\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 164 matches (64 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":164,"truncated":true},"title":"AR-015|picod|PicoD|ÕæĮõ╗żµē¦ĶĪī","time":{"start":1775860280918,"end":1775860280930}}}}
